Engoki o enkitamioto e Yuda


1  “Eigeroki eng'oki e Yuda te nkalamu e sekenkei, ore te ntopij e almasi, etisiraki te mbao oltau lenye, o too mowuarak oo lperereni lenye loo lasarri. 
2  Ina kata edamu nkera enye ilperereni lenye loo lasarri o enkai enye naji Asherim, te mbata e pooki shani onyori, o te nchumata e pooki doinyo adoru, 
3  too nchumat oo ldoinyo te nkop naisiaja. Ore karsisisho ino o lchumat linono pooki kaisho metaari anaa enkinyang'a eng'oki ino, tiatua enkop ino pooki. 
4  Iorore iyie enjung'ore ino apa naaishoo, naa kaaisho nanu iyie isiaayia ilmang'ati linono tiatua enkop nimiyiolo, amu ore te ngoro ai, neinuaaki enkima nayupuyup ntarasi.”

Nkikoot naapaasha


5  Nji ejo Olaitoriani:

“Ediaa oltung'ani oisilig iltung'ana

neitaa osesen le tung'ani emasaai o larrabal.

Ilo oibelekeny oltau lenye aitung'uaa Olaitoriani.


6  Etiu ninye anaa enkiti shani nabulu olpurkel,

nemedol ninye ae sidai elotu.

Keton ninye too worro tiong'ota,

te nkop naisukut nememanya.


7  “Emayiana ilo tung'ani oisilig Olaitoriani,

otii osiligi lenye atua Olaitoriani.


8   Etiu ninye anaa olchani

otunoki te mbata enkare,

oreu ntona enyena embata olkeju,

nemeureishoyu tenelotu enkirowuaj,

amu ketoni ake mbenek enyena enyori,

nemesi ninye te nkata olameyu,

amu mepal ae kata ninye meiu ilng'anayio.”


9  Olalejani oltau alang ntokitin pooki,

naa torrono oleng.

Kaing'ae oidim atayiolo ninye?


10   “Kajur nanu Olaitoriani ndamunot natem oltau,

pee aisho pooki tung'ani te risioroto

oo nkoitoi enyena te risioroto oo lng'anayio loo nkiaasin enyena.”


11  Anaa enkurlee naiturrur nkera

neitu edanyu, neijia eikununo ilo otum

karsisisho kake mme te sipata;

ore te mpolos oo nkolong'i enyena neing'uaa ninche ninye,

ore te nkiting'oto enye neaku olmodai.


12  Olorika le nkitoo le nkisisa otipikaki

apa shumata ebaiki enkiterunoto,

ninye ewueji ang sinyati.


13  Iyie Olaitoriani osiligi le Israel,

ore pooki liking'uaa iyie netum enkurruna;

ore lelo likimbelekenya

aaing'uaa iyie, neigeri tiatua enkop, too kulukuok

amu etanyaita ninche Olaitoriani,

ina ong'u enkare naishu.

Etoomono Yeremia Olaitoriani eretoto


14  Nchiunyeki nanu Olaitoriani, naa kaishiu; ntajeuoki naa kajeu; amu ira iyie enkisisa ai.


15  Ng'ura kaajoki ninche nanu, “Koree ororei oing'uaa Olaitoriani? nchoo elotu!” 
16  Eitu nanu aaitirrishaki iyie pee irriu entorroni, neitu nanu ang'uar enkolong e mutai, iyiolo iyie; ore ina napuku tiatua enkutuk ai netii dukuya enkomom ino. 
17  Meaku olkirutoto te nanu; ira iyie esarunoto ai te nkolong entorroni. 
18  Nchoo metukurru lelo laaisilisil nanu, kake mikincho nanu aaitukurruni. Nchoo ninche eirut, kake mikincho nanu airut! Intadoiki ninche enkolong entorroni; ingilie ninche kat are enkidaata.

Enkibung'ata e Sabato


19  Nji aatiaaka nanu Olaitoriani: “Shomo ntasho te nkishomi e Benchamen, naa ninye ejing'unye ilaiguanak le Yuda naa ninye eipang'ie, o too nchomito pooki e Yerusalem, 
20  nijo, ‘Entoning ororei lo laitoriani intae ilaiguanak le Yuda, o Yuda pooki, o lelo pooki oomanya Yerusalem, oojing'u te kuna shomito. 
21   Nji ejo Olaitoriani: entorripoto tenkaraki enkishui inyi, niminapinapa olola te nkolong e sabato aashu iimunyenye nchomito e Yerusalem. 
22   Niminapinapa olola aaitayu too nkajijik inyi te nkolong e sabato aashu iasiasa ae siaai, kake entaa enkolong e sabato sinyati, anaa apa enaitanapa loo papaai linyi. 
23  Ore eyia eitu apa ninche ening'isho neitu eishoru enkiok enye, kake etogolong'utua, pee mening nemeng'amu inkiteng'enat.


24  “ ‘Kake tenikining'ining'i intae nanu, Olaitoriani ojo, nimintijing'ung'u olola too nchomito ena anasa te nkolong e sabato, kake nintaa enkolong e sabato sinyati nimiasishosho teina olong, 
25  netum aaimu nchomito ena anasa ilaiguanak ootonie olorika le nkitoo le Daudi, ekedito ngarrin oo mbartan o mbartan, ninche o lkituaak lenye, lelo tung'ana le Yuda o lelo oomanya Yerusalem; nemanyi ena anasa ntarasi. 
26  Nepuonu iltung'ana ooing'uaa nkang'itie e Yuda o wuejitin neemanita Yerusalem, eing'uaa enkop e Benchamen, eing'uaa Shefela, eing'uaa ina kop oo ldoinyo, o looing'ua negeb, eyau ilasarri oopejori o nkishorot, nkishorot e nkurma o lbani, neyau nkishorot e nashe enkaji Olaitoriani. 
27  Kake tenimikining'ining'i intae nanu, aaitaa enkolong e sabato sinyati, niminapinapa olola niimumu nchomito e Yerusalem te nkolong e sabato, nainok nanu enkima too nchomito enyena, naa kemut nkajijik e nkitoo e Yerusalem nemeari ae kata.’ ”

